Title: Realization of the Dirac bracket algebras through first class functions

and quantization of constrained systemsComments: 7 pages,Latex,misprints corrected, references added, the material on

the connection between the Dirac bracket and star-product commutator algebrasis addedJournal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 61 (2002) 107-111

It is shown that a Dirac bracket algebra is isomorphic to the originalPoisson bracket algebra of first class functions subject to first classconstraints. The isomorphic image of the Dirac bracket algebra in thestar-product commutator algebra is found.